description: This continuation of Mathematics 120 concentrates on methods and applications of integration and infinite sequences and series. May also include elementary differential equations and multiple integrals. Prerequisite: Mathematics 119 or 120 or 122, or Mathematics Placement Recommendation. Credit may be earned for either Mathematics 126 or 128, but not both.
